## 2025-12-02: Register Page Translations and Validation Implementation

### Task 1: Added translations for register page
- **Files Modified:**
  - `lib/src/languages/translations.dart` - Added 'register' section with 11 keys for all 10 supported languages (uz, uz-Cyrl, ru, en, tr, kaa, tg, kk, ky, tk)
  - `lib/src/languages/strings.dart` - Added 11 string constants for register page
  - `lib/src/ui/pages/hilol_chat_register_page.dart` - Replaced all hardcoded strings with translated keys using Strings class and .tr() method

**Translation keys added:**
- greeting: Welcome message
- instruction: Form instruction text
- name_label: Name field label
- name_placeholder: Name field placeholder
- email_or_phone_label: Email/phone field label
- email_or_phone_placeholder: Email/phone field placeholder
- start_button: Submit button text
- name_required: Validation error for empty name
- name_too_short: Validation error for short name
- email_or_phone_required: Validation error for empty email/phone
- email_or_phone_invalid: Validation error for invalid email/phone format

### Task 2: Implemented form validation with Bloc pattern
- **Files Created:**
  - `lib/src/inputs/name_input.dart` - Formz input validator for name field with empty and too short validation
  - `lib/src/inputs/email_or_phone_input.dart` - Formz input validator for email/phone field with empty and invalid format validation
  - `lib/src/blocs/register/hilol_chat_register_bloc.dart` - Register bloc with validation logic
  - `lib/src/blocs/register/hilol_chat_register_event.dart` - Register events (nameChanged, emailOrPhoneChanged, submit)
  - `lib/src/blocs/register/hilol_chat_register_state.dart` - Register state with form fields and validation status
  - `lib/src/blocs/register/hilol_chat_register_bloc.freezed.dart` - Generated freezed code for bloc

**Bloc Implementation:**
- Used Formz for form validation with pure/dirty states
- Used Freezed for immutable state and events with code generation
- Validation triggers on field changes
- Submit button enabled only when form is valid
- Error messages displayed in real-time using translated strings

**UI Integration:**
- Added BlocProvider at page level to provide bloc instance
- Used BlocBuilder to rebuild UI on state changes
- Connected input fields to bloc events via onChanged callbacks
- Display validation errors from bloc state
- Submit button disabled when form is invalid

### Technical Details:
- Used existing project patterns: bloc + freezed + formz
- Followed existing string extension pattern for translations
- Ran `dart run build_runner build` to generate freezed code
- All 10 languages supported with proper translations
